Covert Skins.name: M4A1-S | Hyper Beast
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a beastly creature in psychadelic colours.
Covert Skins.lore: You really want to impress me Booth? Make this black light sensitive - Rona Sabri, Rising Star

Covert Skins.name: MAC-10 | Neon Rider
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with the image of a deadly biker.
Covert Skins.lore: One part firearm, two parts Trapper Keeper

Classified Skins.name: FAMAS | Djinn
Classified Skins.desc: It has been inlaid with gold and nickel and engraved with the image of a jinn.
Classified Skins.lore: Be careful what you wish for

Classified Skins.name: Galil AR | Eco
Classified Skins.desc: It has been painted white and green and detailed with heat-transfer decals.
Classified Skins.lore: For enough money, Elite Crew will take any cause on as their own

Classified Skins.name: Five-SeveN | Monkey Business
Classified Skins.lore: Sometimes it's ok to play with your food

Restricted Skins.name: AWP | Worm God
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been painted with the image of a skull and roots using high-durability enamel paints.
Restricted Skins.lore: There are some roots you don't want to take hold

Restricted Skins.name: CZ75-Auto | Pole Position
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a red and grey racing theme.
Restricted Skins.lore: We only get one chance at this, let's do it right - Felix Riley, Commanding Officer

Restricted Skins.name: UMP-45 | Grand Prix
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with an old-fashioned racing motif.

Restricted Skins.name: MAG-7 | Heat
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted to look as though it just came out of the forge.
Restricted Skins.lore: Make some outlines of your own

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Negev | Man-o'-war
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been given a base coat of blue metallic paint then hand-painted with metallic gold swirls and accents.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Turn some heads before you take them off

Mil-Spec Skins.name: P250 | Valence
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted in a modern blue and grey design that complements the weapon's form.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Your skills aren't in question, your attitude is - The Teacher and The Iconoclast Part 1

Mil-Spec Skins.name: AK-47 | Elite Build
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted using a combination of hydrographics and careful stenciling and detailed with heat-transfer decals.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Tread softly Naomi...people in your line of work aren't known for their longevity - The Shield and The Serpent Part 2

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MP7 | Armor Core
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted with black oil-based paint and given brushed stainless steel parts and inlay.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Perfect for the Operator that values sophistication as well as firepower - Booth, Arms Dealer

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Sawed-Off | Origami
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with an origami-inspired design.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: It takes time to build something beautiful, but only a moment to destroy it

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Desert Eagle | Bronze Deco
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted in an art deco pattern using metallic automotive paints.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Everyone's searching for silver and gold
